OL,3,CJailed paddleboard instructor sacked
OL,4,Cfrom police for fraudulent claim
OL,6,FA paddleboard operator who was jailed
OL,7,Fafter four people drowned during an
OL,8,Fexcursion on a river in Pembrokeshire
OL,9,Fwas previously sacked as a police
OL,10,Fofficer for making a fraudulent
OL,11,Finsurance claim.
OL,13,FNerys Bethan Lloyd, 39, organised a
OL,14,Fstand-up paddleboarding tour on the
OL,15,FRiver Cleddau in Haverfordwest in
OL,16,FOctober 2021 despite "extremely
OL,17,Fhazardous conditions" and weather
OL,18,Fwarnings.
