OL,6,FLloyd, who was jailed for ten years
OL,7,Fand six months at Swansea Crown Court
OL,8,Flast week, failed to warn the group
OL,9,Fabout a dangerous weir with a 1.3m
OL,10,Fdrop along the route, or how to
OL,11,Fnavigate it.
OL,13,FPaul O'Dwyer, 42, Andrea Powell, 41,
OL,14,FNicola Wheatley, 40 and Morgan Rogers,
OL,15,F24 all died as they were swept over,
OL,16,Fbecoming trapped under the fast-moving
OL,17,Fwater.
