OL,3,CJailed paddleboard instructor sacked
OL,4,Cfrom police for fraudulent claim
OL,6,FAfter the sentencing, South Wales
OL,7,FPolice published details of a
OL,8,Fmisconduct hearing which led to her
OL,9,Fdismissal as an officer in 2022.
OL,11,FIt revealed that she claimed #577.55
OL,12,Fto cover a car repair that only cost
OL,13,Faround #16 to #20.
OL,15,FLloyd admitted her wrongdoing,
OL,16,Fapologised and said it was an error of
OL,17,Fjudgment and repaid the amount in
OL,18,Ffull, the misconduct hearing was told.
