OL,3,CJailed paddleboard instructor sacked
OL,4,Cfrom police for fraudulent claim
OL,6,FShe was interviewed under caution on
OL,7,FOctober 11 2021, two weeks before the
OL,8,Fpaddleboarding incident.
OL,10,FLloyd attended Ystrad Mynach Police
OL,11,FStation on October 19 2021 and
OL,12,Faccepted a formal caution for the
OL,13,Fcriminal offence of fraud by false
OL,14,Frepresentation under the Fraud Act
OL,15,F2006.
OL,17,FChief Constable Jeremy Vaughan said in
OL,18,Fhis decision: "It is entirely
OL,19,Funacceptable for police officers, who
OL,20,Fare responsible for enforcing the law,
OL,21,Fto break the law themselves."
