OL,3,CJailed paddleboard instructor sacked
OL,4,Cfrom police for fraudulent claim
OL,6,FAfter the river incident, Lloyd sought
OL,7,Fto blame Mr O'Dwyer, who helped act as
OL,8,Fan instructor on the trip.
OL,10,FSpeaking outside the court, Theresa
OL,11,FHall, the mother of Morgan Rogers,
OL,12,Fsaid she lost her "best friend" and
OL,13,Fcould "never forgive" Lloyd.
OL,15,FDarren Wheatley, Ms Wheatley's
OL,16,Fhusband, said the loss of his wife was
OL,17,Fdue to Lloyd and no one else.
