OL,6,F"There were nine people on the river
OL,7,Fthat day and every one of them is a
OL,8,Fvictim."
OL,10,FLloyd, from Aberavon was the owner and
OL,11,Fsole director of Salty Dog Co Ltd,
OL,12,Fwhich organised the tour.
